short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Skip Death Screens in Gaming Videos

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension lets you skip deaths in League of Legends and Smite videos.

It functions just like the Netflix skip intro button -- whenever the guy in the video dies, a little button pops up, giving you the choice to skip to the moment that he respawns.

It works automatically for every League of Legends and Smite video on youtube.

Source: github.com/darbyhaller/skipper_ext/
Twitter: twitter.com/youtubeskipper
